title: Creative Outlier ONE Wireless Bluetooth 4.1, IPX4 Water-Resistant Sweat-Proof in-Ear Headphones with Built-in Microphone, 9.5 Hours Battery Life and Tangle-Free Cable (Black)
feature: WIRELESS BLUETOOTH, HIGH DEFINITION AUDIO | High definition Bluetooth 4.1 consumes low power with minimal latency. Reach new heights in your fitness with the specially tuned 6mm Neodymium drivers that keep your music pumping.
